3. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the development of a systems thinking framework for cybersecurity modeling, which can be related to software engineering. 
4. cs.CY (Computers and Society) - The paper discusses the impact of cybersecurity on society and proposes a systems thinking approach to tackle cybersecurity challenges, which can be related to computers and society. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the use of systems thinking as a tool for cybersecurity modeling, which can be related to artificial intelligence.
